{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6f35d5f87d","title":"毛泽东关于召开县以下各级干部会议等问题给王任重的两封信","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"08efdcd53e","index":0,"year":1959,"month":3,"day":16,"articleId":"6f35d5f87d"}],"tags":[{"id":"8b05ac46d8","name":"王任重","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ce3a5a91f9","type":"title","text":"毛泽东关于召开县以下各级干部会议等问题给王任重的两封信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f35d5f87d"},{"id":"3435239074","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f35d5f87d"},{"id":"eba7282d62","type":"appellation","text":"任重同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f35d5f87d"},{"id":"f151812bf5","type":"paragraph","text":"今日上午，请找各地委第一书记及几个县委书记商量一下：省的会议以后，是否应以几天时间召开县的四级或五级干部会议，此种会议应到些什么人，应开几天；然后再开公社代表大会，应到些什么人，应开几天，是否应选举社的管理委员会(其成员如何组成)。下午，我们再商量一下。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f35d5f87d"},{"id":"8a506037df","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东三月十六日上午二时","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f35d5f87d"},{"id":"34db1fc6ed","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f35d5f87d"},{"id":"ad75848ed2","type":"appellation","text":"任重同志：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f35d5f87d"},{"id":"392dba693d","type":"paragraph","text":"送上文件24件，极有味，好读。我劝你于今天上午看一遍，一气看完，有3—4小时就够了。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f35d5f87d"},{"id":"f3dcab02a8","type":"paragraph","text":"下午你再找地委书记少数县委书记座谈，谈县、区、乡、村如何开会问题。我们晚上再交谈。以为如何?花费这一天，不是于湖北工作没有用的，你试一试看吧!","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6f35d5f87d"},{"id":"f575afe837","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东三月十六日上午七时","index":9,"p